abstract: Nicolas Colsaerts takes lead in Italian Open with nine-under-par 63.
lead_paragraph: Nicolas Colsaerts had eight straight birdies and finished with a nine-under-par 63 to take the lead in the Italian Open at Golf Club Milano in Monza.

headline.main: Colsaerts Sets Pace at Italian Open With a 63
